input: Conduct a structured audit analysis to pinpoint financial risks and compliance issues, recommend revisions, and deliver both technical and executive summary reports.

subtasks.input: Establish audit boundaries, objectives, and success criteria through stakeholder consultation and regulatory requirement mapping.
Extract financial records, compliance documentation, and operational metrics from source systems while performing initial data quality checks.
